column2: SELECT TOP #    p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,p.extinction_i    ISNULL(s.specobjid,#) AS specobjid, ISNULL(s.z, #) AS zs ,ISNULL(s.class, #) AS class , ISNULL(s.subclass, #) AS subclass FROM PhotoObj AS p    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid FROM WISE_allsky as Wi   JOIN w1mag AS w1 and w2mag AS w2 ON w1.coadd_id = p.objid
